{"tid":1606955,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真岳巴獨家宣言 - 我只是一個香港人","createTime":"2019-09-30T16:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T17:38:21.000Z","uid":68738,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a580374453f94ee8f9355828403484d40b80c408","tid":1606955,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:45:38.000Z","msg":"真岳巴獨家宣言 - 我只是一個香港人<br />\n<br />\n各位香港人大家好<br />\n多謝連日來你地對我傷勢嘅關心<br />\n(頭部7針+身體各部分都有瘀傷)<br />\n而家慢慢康復緊<br />\n希望大家唔會太擔心<br />\n<br />\n由於我既事已經進入司法程序<br />\n所以我不便多說希望大家明白<br />\n<br />\n跟住我要多謝<br />\n一班係我背後支持關心我既<br />\n家人朋友老師同各大媒體<br />\n<br />\n而律師方面，都已經得到足夠支援<br />\n同時家人亦給與我好大的支持，<br />\n所以法律支援同生活喺呢一刻都唔成問題<br />\n大家唔需要捐款比我 亦唔需要太擔心<br />\n<br />\n有鑒於「近日」網上有人發動籌款幫我<br />\n我想重申呢一刻我並無冇呢個需要<br />\n如果大家真係想捐款 可以捐款去612基金或者星火<br />\n<br />\n喺網上得知有人提議組成「岳家軍」<br />\n其實香港人冇需要岳家軍 <br />\n只係需要一班出嚟關心香港既人<br />\n而件衫只係一個行山品牌絕對冇特別意思<br />\n<br />\n見到網上面對我有好多不同的稱呼<br />\n有⼈叫我做「英雄」「義士」<br />\n但我想講我只是一個普通既香港人<br />\n係一個同大家共同進退既手足<br />\n<br />\n之前有⼿足想燒山<br />\n我都呼籲大家要好好地保護香港的郊野土地<br />\n香港郊野有好多獨有原生物種及係候鳥棲息地，<br />\n香港土地都係我地需要愛惜<br />\n<br />\n目前網上消息太多，<br />\n大家覺得有懷疑的時候<br />\n可以fact check 先<br />\n關於有朋友替我出post而引起公眾誤會、麻煩 <br />\n我想喺度講聲唔好意思。<br />\n<br />\n各位⼿足「留得青山在，那怕沒柴燒」<br />\n唔好因為一時既困境而走上絕路<br />\n要堅持，珍惜生命，先會勝利<br />\n<br />\n最後我想同香港人講<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港、時代革命<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n#PPPN #真岳巴 #香港人 #以曝止暴<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PPPNinternation/videos/430757994457685?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPPPNinternation%2Fvideos%2F430757994457685%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6t3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=c9df3c6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PPPNinternation/videos/430757994457685?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"a41c6f7e930aef81edfcb603c335fbe680a521ce","tid":1606955,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:46:42.000Z","msg":"好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2bb9e58bacae66a646342ca9c057ec141778093","tid":1606955,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d3a1f3c15792bafc0e236dd4090f144c2d5d9e","tid":1606955,"uid":172093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:58:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7ec4382d268008c74b248f617a20197c2ffd8c04","tid":1606955,"uid":79200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:05:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6ba3aafd0d544042a4cc9993a8d8fedfcb0d5095","tid":1606955,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:06:33.000Z","msg":"謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559294eddd560cdf3c113bfd914e05d01eeec01a","tid":1606955,"uid":109706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"357c710a01998e7b2362a05d411e0f74f1c43da6","tid":1606955,"uid":139677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:12:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dd13aa0913fb5136fc4e3c522d7e6b2ad5aa0316","tid":1606955,"uid":279236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"攬實老公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0545efacab2ce86366ab699ef1f12b1abf7f4da","tid":1606955,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:15:13.000Z","msg":"real oppa"},{"pid":"8c2933e17503c3e54a1c3bbc1b9f367bf1e36a46","tid":1606955,"uid":291465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:17:03.000Z","msg":"岳巴加油"},{"pid":"c1fd9899443c3bd981962e02d27b58fdab9faebe","tid":1606955,"uid":161711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:24:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c263f605b4db6441c09f0e08ad66dd3b253063a9","tid":1606955,"uid":74418,"l